+‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ test_database.py           # Database layer tests (CRUD operations)
+‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ test_api_endpoints.py      # API integration tests (HTTP endpoints)
+```
+
+## Running Tests
+
+### Run All Tests
+```bash
+cd backend
+chmod +x run_tests.sh
+./run_tests.sh
+```
+
+### Run Individual Tests
+
+**Database Layer Only:**
+```bash
+source .venv/bin/activate
+python tests/test_database.py
+```
+
+**API Endpoints Only** (requires server running):
+```bash
+# Terminal 1: Start server
+source .venv/bin/activate
+python server.py
+
+# Terminal 2: Run tests
+source .venv/bin/activate
+python tests/test_api_endpoints.py
+```
+
+## Test Coverage
+
+### Database Layer (`test_database.py`)
+- ‚úÖ Get system decks
+- ‚úÖ Get deck with voices
+- ‚úÖ Fork deck (system ‚Üí user)
+- ‚úÖ Update deck (user-owned)
+- ‚úÖ Create voice in user deck
+- ‚úÖ Update voice (user-owned)
+- ‚úÖ Fork voice to user deck
+- ‚úÖ Delete voice (user-owned)
+- ‚úÖ Delete deck with cascade (user-owned)
+
+### API Endpoints (`test_api_endpoints.py`)
+- ‚úÖ Authentication (register/login)
+- ‚úÖ GET /api/decks (list all)
+- ‚úÖ GET /api/decks/{id} (get with voices)
+- ‚úÖ POST /api/decks/{id}/fork (fork deck)
+- ‚úÖ PUT /api/decks/{id} (update deck)
+- ‚úÖ DELETE /api/decks/{id} (delete deck)
+- ‚úÖ POST /api/voices (create voice)
+- ‚úÖ PUT /api/voices/{id} (update voice)
+- ‚úÖ DELETE /api/voices/{id} (delete voice)
+- ‚úÖ POST /api/voices/{id}/fork (fork voice)
+- ‚úÖ Permission checks (401/404 for unauthorized)
+
+## Requirements
+
+- Python virtual environment with dependencies
+- SQLite database (auto-created if missing)
+- Port 8765 available for test server
+
+## Troubleshooting
+
+**"Server failed to start"**
+- Check if port 8765 is already in use: `lsof -i:8765`
+- Kill existing process: `lsof -ti:8765 | xargs kill -9`
+- Check `models.json` exists in backend directory
+
+**"Database tests failed"**
+- Ensure database is properly initialized: `python database.py`
+- Check database file permissions
+
+**"API tests return 502"**
+- Server may have crashed - check `/tmp/test_server.log`
+- Verify PolyCLI is installed: `pip show polycli`
